Class RequestTableView

  • java.lang.Object
    • Entity.RequestTableView

  • public class RequestTableView
extends java.lang.Object
    Build Table View use the FXML components from this class only.
    make new class with no parameters and you will get the table ready for use.
    use function onRequirementClicked for get selected row in the table.
    list of fxml can use:
  • tblViewRequests - the table
  • columnId
  • columnStatus
  • columnStage
  • columnDueTime
  • columnMessage
  • columnInitiator
  • columnStartDate
  • columnSystem
  • columnProblemDescription
  • columnWhyChange
  • columnComment
  • columnDoc
